extends layout

block content
  h2 Welcome to Comments by Real People

  //Reject empty fields, enforce a maximum character length, and sanitize input to prevent XSS.

  //Pagination/lazy loading: >10 comments, do a load more button/comment pages

  //Error handling: display meaningful error messages (no raw error codes or stack traces)

  //done: timestamp

  ol
  each val in todos
    li
      span= val.task + ' - ' + val.formattedDate
      form(method='POST' action='/delete')
        input(type='hidden', name='id', value=val.id)
        button(type='submit') Delete

  hr
  h2 Comment:
  form(method='POST' action='/create')
    //label(for='task') Task:
    input(type='text', name='task', id='task', required, maxlength="250")
    button(type='submit') Submit
